children.text: Enough Said spoken word series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on February 27, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Lee Gotham accompanied by Sam Shalabi, and Ann Diamond. Open mic/supporting performances by Beau Williamson, Jen Frankel, Vince Tinguely, Graham Olds, Ran Elfassy, Thoth Harris, Halina Berger, R. M. Vaughan, Scott Duncan, Justin McGrail, and Ran Elfassy and more.
